Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の“その笑顔”だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「谢谢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠过树梢的阳光 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝天 白云 漫漫长路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同样渺小的存在 只要手牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心怀更壮大的梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多么宽大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就算特制的望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因为世界上最棒的景点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是时刻绽放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪伴我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充满心中的这份心情 总是说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小阳春 赞♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻译：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 四个人 需要预定餐食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山小屋预订好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}√买方便食品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}√预定山肩登山小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登谷川岳的准备就妥妥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容也好可爱 简直完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的吗 谢谢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.23,0:02:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵可真厉害 完全能独当一面了呢 超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光学姐太过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…刚这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假作业写了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.13,title,NTP,0,0,0,,作业写不完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全上垒！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业！只字未动呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多 可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,186)\fad(100,0)\c&H0E193A&\3c&HF1F9FF&\shad0}兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(912,108)\fad(100,0)\c&H0E193A&\3c&HF1F9FF&\shad0}登山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,318)\fad(100,0)\c&H0E193A&\3c&HF1F9FF&\shad0}手工
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,574)\fad(100,0)\c&H0E193A&\3c&HF1F9FF&\shad0}捉虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\c&H0E193A&\3c&HF1F9FF&\shad0\pos(128,602)}睡午觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又爬山又兼职 玩得倒是尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一没写作业露馅了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业啊 没事的 我有在写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 有写就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上初中的时候每次都拖到最后才想起赶作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事的 我打算去谷川岳之前 就全写完的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵真长大了呢 上了高中就是不一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进一步自掘坟墓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱们吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想办法蒙混过关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业写完了给妈妈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始写咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上学期学这个了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是那个骑马爬富士山的谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家吃不下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小葵怎么没精神了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人每次都贴得好近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.48,0:04:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假作业剩下好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很忧郁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业啊 好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学生可轻松啦 没作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光学姐上高中时也为作业发愁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不过和朋友一起写就都写完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白的地方大家相互教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友…这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 日向啊 要不要一起写作业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你肯定没写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在在白浜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.81,yama_neta,NTP,0,0,0,,白浜 和歌山县古来有名的海滨温泉圣地 夏天适宜洗海水浴 是休闲旅游的名所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个白浜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南纪白浜温泉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说以前人都来这度蜜月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全日本都来这度蜜月 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说爸爸妈妈结婚的时候也来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次结婚纪念日就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫冒险世界的游乐园 那里还有熊猫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑黑的 白白的 可可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别说熊猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应妈妈去谷川岳之前把作业全写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我作业都写完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我两三天就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我给你带好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个破日向 竟然自己就把作业写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她说她当家教来着 期末考试也名列前茅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一脸傻相 但学习倒是很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算借来抄等她回来也来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那家伙怎么想也不是那种轻易把作业给我抄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写完作业去攀登回忆中的高峰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南纪白浜最棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！你给我等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我把作业收拾完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写不完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 小枫学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先写哪科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先写数学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这道题不会做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 这道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怪 去年学这些了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道课程内容变了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要先来别的科目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那古文…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小枫学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小枫学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒昧问一下 您自己的作业写完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思 其实我也只字未动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来以为高一的作业能帮帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没关系！别担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给谁打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜酱一定会教我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是初中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的 人家可是可可娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得她没问题 但让初中生帮着做作业也太糗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道小枫学姐的朋友怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿不要太凶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教 我叫友香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小葵 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的人啊 看起来人也不错 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对！要把那边的数字代入进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你光顾着爬山都不好好听课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计算太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许抱怨 看 那边算错了 字真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连我都得受教育
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵有不懂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这道题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是小枫学姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对小枫学姐很严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过人很聪明 又很会教人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月日は百代の過客にして 行きかふ年も又旅人也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舟の上に生涯を浮かべ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:37.18,yama_neta,NTP,0,0,0,,选自俳人松尾芭蕉见闻游记『奥之细道（奥の細道）』序文 也是该文集中最为著名的一句 意为「日月是永远的过客 来去匆匆的时间也像旅行者一般 人生飘荡在行船中的船夫 和与马同行迎来晚年的马夫 他们的每一天都在旅途中渡过 旅途就是他们的归宿」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您点的巧克力蛋糕和拿破仑蛋糕各一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这里 lead拼错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写作业 做兼职 每一天都很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写完啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能这么快写完 多亏了友香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢友香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们下学期开始要好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是小枫 明明脑子挺好 但总是偷懒没干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得人家都不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁夸你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是全靠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友香学姐讲得很好 非常好懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的？那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像老师一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 讲得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去那座山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏友香学姐帮忙 答应妈妈的事没有违约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看你看 都晒成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南纪白浜真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了攀登回忆中的那座山嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以全身心投入谷川岳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就剩下克服恐高症坐缆车了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪壶不开提哪壶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着越来越短的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿能留下最美的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:04.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,晴れた日も 雨の日も しあわせだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,また明日 あたらしい 空に描こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:16.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,消えない Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,紙と色鉛筆だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:31.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな夢も叶えられた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,子供の頃の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,取り戻したような日々
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:47.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,楽しかった季節ひとつが終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:55.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,まっしろなスケジュール 落書きで埋めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,12色パレットじゃ描けない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心に焼きついてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなひと100人にいつか見せたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,花咲くアシアト
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,晴れた日も 雨の日も しあわせだったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,天気予報はいらないね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,軽やかに 歩き出す 道の向こうに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:28.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心色 Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:04.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无论晴天还是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.82,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就不需要天气预报了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:16.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在明天新的晨光中画下永不褪色的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:31.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,只用纸和彩铅 就能实现所有愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:38.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都仿佛重拾儿时的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:47.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愉快的季节告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:55.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,用涂鸦填满雪白的日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,十二色的调色板 画不尽的世界 永远烙在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 分享给100个我爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,鲜花盛开的足迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,无论晴天还是雨天 如果都有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就不需要天气预报了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:28.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,轻快地迈开脚步 道路的远方 是心中的彩虹
